Depends: kernel (=6.6.69~48e2cdbcb753cc975d51caf79f3eba4e-r1), kmod-crypto-lib-chacha20poly1305, kmod-crypto-lib-curve25519, kmod-udptunnel4, kmod-udptunnel6
